                            </bibl>
                            <bibl>See sub classmark <idno>A. 41</idno> in "Further Notes on
                                the Literature of the Hurufis and Their Connection with the Bektashi
                                Order of Dervishes Author(s): Edward G. Browne Source: The Journal
                                of the Royal Asiatic Society of Great Britain and Ireland , Jul.,
